  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in Senate", 
    "date": "2015-01-13T05:00:00Z", 
    "text": "No Tax Write-offs for Corporate Wrongdoers Act\n\nAmends the Internal Revenue Code to: (1) deny a tax deduction for any amount paid or incurred for punitive damages in connection with any judgment in, or settlement of, any legal action; and (2) include any amount paid as punitive damages in gross income for income tax purposes."
